name: FloryBelle
description: An app about taking care of plants.

bodyParagraphs.title: About Project
bodyParagraphs.body:
An app about helping students take care of their plants. It will give them detailed information about their plant's needs and will help them keep their plants alive.

They can scan their plants using their camera and the app will show them information about the moisture it needs, sunlight levels, soil quality, and room temperature.

bodyParagraphs.title: Problem Statement
bodyParagraphs.body: A lot of people are not being able to take care of their plants properly, do not understand their needs which leads to them dying our of unproper care.
